<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Isu chanchin hezaw diek ka,
 A lungsietna midang hilh ka;
 A hukdamna bukim mu'ng ka,
 Kei dinga Thipa hehpihna.

[V2]
 Isu hezaw diek ka (2)
 A hukdamna bukim mung ka,
 Kei dinga Thipa hehpihna.

[V3]
 2. Isu chanchin ei hilh hen la,
 A thienthona hezaw diek ka;
 Thagau ei sinsakpa hi hen,
 Krista thilhaw ei hilh hen la.

[V4]
 3. Isu chanchin chu A thu-ah,
 Ka Lalpa chu tawh kivawp in;
 Mun chenga Amah Aw chuh za'n,
 A thugen cheng ginum, kei di'n.

[V5]
 4. A chutphah a Lalpa Isu,
 Neihzawh, lopina Amah a;
 A gam lopina khawk diek ding,
 Chamna Lal Chapa hung ni chun.</lyrics>
<title>MORE ABOUT JESUS</title>
<hymn_number>193</hymn_number>
</song>